{
  "stem": "5275.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tubbermans ?] when there was a [NON-ENGLISH] in one of those places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The building was filled with SS people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think Werhmacht too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they yelled to us to go down on the streets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was pouring rain.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I guess I didn't move fast enough, because one of the soldiers-- and I don't know how I know this, but he was Ukrainian in the Werhmacht, felt that I was going too slow.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he took the butt of his gun, and he hit me right here over the nose, breaking my nose.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I ran with my mother downstairs and stayed in a line of hundreds of people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Germans started two groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One group would go into the train to the Umschlagplatz, and the other group would go back to the factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My mother spoke excellent German, and I think that saved us at that moment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because as we got to the control people, she had this [GERMAN], and she spoke to them in German, saying that we are working there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they motioned us to go back to the factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What I remember from that particular moment was a-- a family in front of me-- a father, mother, and two little children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the Germans, for some reason, told-- pushed the mother towards the Umschlagplatz row, and the father and the children to the factory.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the father said, I cannot take care of these children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he joined with the mother to Umschlagplatz with those two children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I thought this was absolutely horrible on his part, you know, to do this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And then there was a second night-- I don't know why it was always raining-- in which they did get us to the Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
